      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀大王，慢些慢些。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00024",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "怎么要慢些？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00025",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "咱们这卧龙山，不斩无名之人。问他家乡哪里，姓甚名谁。那时将他杀了，也知道一个名字。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00026",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "你前去问来。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00027",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "是。呔，黑汉，我大王问你，家乡哪里，姓甚名谁？对我讲了，我好去禀我大王。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00028",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四喽兵"
      ],
      "text": "呔，禀大王……",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00029",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "呔，先将你强盗名姓讲来。我便言俺的家乡。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00030",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "哦？你要问我大王姓名。你们退下了。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00031",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四喽兵"
      ],
      "text": "吓。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00032",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四喽兵同下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00033",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "待我讲来你听。我大王乃湖广房州人氏，父名纪德，自幼在此落草。父母亡故，她便作了大王。我的话说完了，请你讲。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00034",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "呔，站开些。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00035",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "哦，我就站开些。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00036",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，且住。他乃绿林中人，俺就通了名性，料也无妨。呔，站过来。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00037",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00038",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "提起俺的威名，只恐吓破你们苦胆。你且听了。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00039",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "家住绛州龙门县，迁移长安御驾前。祖父白袍薛仁贵，跨海征东十二年。镇国一品樊氏母，父讳丁山掌兵权。所生弟兄人四个，猛、勇、刚、强世袭官。俺名薛刚通城虎，英雄无敌天下传。",
      "text_length": 83
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00040",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "是、是、是，我明白了。待我禀过大王。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00041",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "问来没有？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00042",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "问来了。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00043",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "什么名姓？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00044",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "提起威名，吓破你的苦胆。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00045",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "讲来。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00046",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "他乃绛州龙门人氏，先祖薛仁贵，父名丁山，母亲樊氏，镇国夫人，兄弟四个，猛、勇、刚、强，世袭王爵。他名薛刚，混号通城虎。大王你怕不怕？",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00047",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "哦！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00048",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "这是天意随人愿，月老匹配美姻缘。急忙松绑陪笑脸，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00049",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "吓，将军。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00050",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "怎么？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00051",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "军卒无知犯尊颜。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00052",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "爵主请坐。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00053",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00054",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "喽啰无知，望乞恕罪！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00055",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00056",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "请问爵主，不在长安，为何路过荒山？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00057",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "只为正月十五夜，大闹花灯，踢死殿下，惊坏朝廷。是我在人丛中打出，独行至此。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00058",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "可知老王爷一家之事否？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00059",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "俺只顾逃走，并不知家内吉凶。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00060",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "吓，爵主，奴有一言，不好启齿。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00061",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "有话请讲。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00062",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "这个……",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00063",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "这个什么？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00064",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00065",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "朱唇未启红上脸，羞人答答怎好言。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00066",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "吓，纪申。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00067",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00068",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "你可知道吓？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00069",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "知道什么？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00070",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "你大王今年一十七岁吓。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00071",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "谁与大王作生日吗？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00072",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "你大王尚未婚配。今见薛爵主武艺高强，若是错过，何处择选。要留他在此做一寨主。命你前去说来，重重赏你。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00073",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "做寨主……可还有什么？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00074",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "哎，附耳上来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00075",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "哦。我明白了，明白了。吓，爵主。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00076",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "什么？",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00077",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "恭喜恭喜。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00078",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "喜从何来？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00079",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "我大王见爵主英雄，欲偕白首。今日相会，乃前世良缘，婚姻大事，不要错过。爵主料难推辞。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00080",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "且慢。哎呀，我又无栖身之地，不免允从此事，再打听爹娘吉凶。呔，俺无聘礼，怎好婚配？",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00081",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "待我禀过大王。启大王：他便允从，只是无有聘礼。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00082",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "只要爵主允从，不用聘礼。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00083",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "是。大王说：只要爵主允从，不用聘礼。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00084",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "不用聘礼，请你大王近前。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00085",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "是。请大王近前。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00086",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "吓，将军。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00087",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "夫人。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00088",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "请坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00089",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "承蒙夫人不弃，只是即要差人打听我家的吉凶。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00090",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "件件依从。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00091",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "请大王夫人下面更衣，好拜花烛。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00092",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "夫人请。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00093",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00094",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "男英女杰岂寻常，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00095",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "纪鸾英"
      ],
      "text": "姻缘千里隔家乡。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00096",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "今日婚配偕白首，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00097",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "来年生个小大王。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00098",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛刚"
      ],
      "text": "好，有赏。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00099",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "纪申"
      ],
      "text": "谢大王。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006044_e00100",
      "play_id": "02006044",
      "scene_id": "02006044_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
